## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="4f888-102">Используйте <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> действие с <xref:System.Windows.EventTrigger> или <xref:System.Windows.Trigger> в интерактивном режиме остановить <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4f888-102">Use a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> action with an <xref:System.Windows.EventTrigger> or <xref:System.Windows.Trigger> to interactively stop a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="4f888-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> влияет только на <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> когда она активна (после <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> запускает).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4f888-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> only affects a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> when it is active (after the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> starts).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4f888-104">Остановка триггеры раскадровки <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentGlobalSpeedInvalidated> и <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentStateInvalidated> события, но не <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Completed> события.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4f888-104">Stopping a storyboard triggers the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentGlobalSpeedInvalidated> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentStateInvalidated> events, but not the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Completed> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="4f888-105"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> не ссылается <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> напрямую.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4f888-105"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> does not reference a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> directly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4f888-106">Вместо этого <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> должна ссылаться <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> из <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> , который управляет <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4f888-106">Rather, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> must reference the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> of the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> that controls the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4f888-107">В разделе [как: использование триггеров событий для управления раскадровкой после ее запуска](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts.md) в качестве примера.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4f888-107">See [How to: Use Event Triggers to Control a Storyboard After It Starts](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts.md) for an example.</span></span>  
  
## <a name="pause-resume-stop-or-otherwise-control-a-storyboard-interactively"></a><span data-ttu-id="4f888-108">Приостановить, возобновить, остановить или интерактивного управления раскадровкой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4f888-108">Pause, Resume, Stop, or Otherwise Control a Storyboard Interactively</span></span>  
 <span data-ttu-id="4f888-109">Чтобы иметь возможность приостанавливать, возобновлять или управление <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> интерактивно, устанавливать <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> свойство его <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> и использовать <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ControllableStoryboardAction> объекта (таких как <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ResumeStoryboard>, или <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard>) управлять им с ссылки на его <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4f888-109">To be able to pause, resume, or otherwise control a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> interactively, set the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> property of its <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> and use a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ControllableStoryboardAction> object (such as <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ResumeStoryboard>, or <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard>) to control it by referencing its <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4f888-110">Если <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> из <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> не указан, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> не может управлять в интерактивном режиме после его начала.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4f888-110">If the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> of <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> is unspecified, the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> cannot be interactively controlled after it is begun.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4f888-111">В разделе [как: использование триггеров событий для управления раскадровкой после ее запуска](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts.md) для получения дополнительной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4f888-111">See [How to: Use Event Triggers to Control a Storyboard After It Starts](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts.md) for more information.</span></span>  
  
